— 
<collectingCountry id="F37A760B1C39FFABA216F8BCA092173F" box="[374,506,1809,1835]" name="Kazakhstan" pageId="11" pageNumber="262">Kazakhstan</collectingCountry>
, Toksanbai range, South Dzungaria Mountains (currently known from the 
<typeStatus id="54D688391C39FFABA61BF8BCA4C3173F" box="[1403,1451,1809,1835]" pageId="11" pageNumber="262">type</typeStatus>
locality only).
</paragraph>
